# Shared Core

Common infrastructure, security, and logic used across the LicensePanel ecosystem.

## Installation for Development

From the root of any sub-project (ApiLicense, Infrastructure/Core, etc.), run:

```bash
pip install -e ../shared_core
```

This ensures that changes in this directory are reflected immediately across all projects without needing re-installation.
